1.19
log
@fruncate() returns EFBIG when length exceeds the max file size.

ok mpi@@
@
text
@.\"	$OpenBSD: truncate.2,v 1.18 2015/09/10 17:55:21 schwarze Exp $
.\"	$NetBSD: truncate.2,v 1.7 1995/02/27 12:39:00 cgd Exp $
.\"
